text: "Life Ante Itta Vundaala" is a 2022 Indian Telugu-language song by singers Geetha Madhuri and Rahul Sipligunj. The song features Pooja Hegde as lead, alongside Venkatesh and Varun Tej. ==Production== It was composed by Devi Sri Prasad from the 2018 soundtrack album F3 of the film of the same name. The song is written by Kasarla Shyam. The song features Pooja Hegde as lead, alongside Venkatesh and Varun Tej. ==Release== The song was released on 17 May 2022. The song received positive response. == References == == Other websites == * Category:2022 songs Category:Pooja Hegde songs
